name: se.zifro.kjell
description:
UI extension of Zifro Playground UI and is used in all Zifro Kjell games.

Requires the Zifro Mellis Compiler and Zifro Playground UI.
Add as dependency to your Packages/manifest.json:

"se.zifro.mellis": "https://github.com/zardan/compiler.git#upm","se.zifro.ui": "https://github.com/zardan/ui.git#upm",
